reviews.review_text: no review from west coast shows 85 was was one of better years of the 80s the whole summer tour the band was firing on all cylinders /  playing  into playing was allways a treat  hightime    comes a time  and she belong to me   jerry broke  out  in 85  they were played then droped   hearts and soul was left on the stage this night when jerry sang she belongs to me  2 encore
